\begin{frame}{Data Augmentation}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Technique to increase the diversity of training data without collecting new data
        \item Commonly used in image, text, and audio processing
        \item Helps reduce overfitting and improve generalization
        \item Especially useful for deep learning models
    \end{itemize}
\end{frame}

